response.overview: Kenneth Feinberg, a powerful D.C. lawyer appointed Special Master of the 9/11 Fund, fights off the cynicism, bureaucracy, and politics associated with administering government funds and, in doing so, discovers what life is worth.
response.tagline: Our national tragedy. Their personal suffering. His impossible task.
response.title: Worth

titles.title: Сколько стоит жизнь. [What Is Life Worth (2020)]
Worth - Was ist ein Leben wert?
